      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the version of me that actually had dreams and a future... he died a long time ago. now i'm just kind of a ghost haunting my own life. just going through the motions of a body that doesn't belong to anyone anymore.",
